Type: Package
Package: SlakeItEasy
Title: Image-Based Estimation of Soil Aggregate Stability
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: Nate Looker
Maintainer: Nate Looker <nlooker@soilhealthinstitute.org>
Description: Utility functions to determine the projected area of soil
    during slaking tests, following Fajardo et al. (2016)
    <doi:10.1016/j.still.2016.05.018>. Functions are designed for output
    of high-throughput image aquisition schemes (e.g., multiple
    replicates, multiple samples).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://soilhealthinstitute.org/,
    https://github.com/Soil-Health-Institute
